1
00:02:16,119 --> 00:02:17,240
Not eating again.

2
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:19,679
Linlang, this child...

3
00:02:19,919 --> 00:02:21,600
I watched her grow up.

4
00:02:21,839 --> 00:02:22,880
You are her friend.

5
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,479
Even if I believe you killed someone,

6
00:02:24,559 --> 00:02:25,759
it would only be out of helplessness.

7
00:02:25,839 --> 00:02:27,360
But you still have to eat.

8
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,000
Otherwise, before the officials arrive,

9
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,520
you might already be gone.

10
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:51,279
From now on, you’ll be my best friend.

11
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:53,039
Sorry, I’m a coroner.

12
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:54,399
I only trust evidence.

13
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,919
Now even my only friend doesn’t trust me.

14
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,160
Lu Jiu.

15
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:15,240
Lu Jiu.

16
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:17,240
You can scold me however you want.

17
00:03:17,839 --> 00:03:19,160
I’m just doing my duty.

18
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:19,919
I have no choice.

19
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,880
Your duty

20
00:03:22,679 --> 00:03:23,720
is to punish evil and promote good.

21
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:24,839
To uncover the truth.

22
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:26,559
Why believe the illusion before you?

23
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,080
I don’t want to believe it either.

24
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,360
But the evidence... Leave.

25
00:03:59,039 --> 00:03:59,759
Sir.

26
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:01,559
Xu Linlang, you’re going to scare me to death.

27
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,679
I found something wrong with Lu Jiu’s case.

28
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:07,520
I’ve been an official for many years.

29
00:04:07,559 --> 00:04:08,919
I don’t need you to teach me how to investigate.

30
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,279
I discovered

31
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:12,320
someone wants to poison Lu Jiu’s food.

32
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:14,240
Lu Jiu’s case is already closed.

33
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,199
The person who would do this

34
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:16,880
must be the real murderer.

35
00:04:17,119 --> 00:04:17,799
I suspect

36
00:04:17,880 --> 00:04:19,359
he’s afraid the case might change.

37
00:04:19,559 --> 00:04:21,200
So he wants to kill to silence the witness.

38
00:04:27,559 --> 00:04:28,359
This matter

39
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:29,760
Is there anyone else who knows about it?

40
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:31,920
I only told Zhao, the head constable who watches over Lu Jiu.

41
00:04:32,239 --> 00:04:33,679
He said Lu Jiu's meals

42
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,959
are all prepared by the kitchen at the yamen.

43
00:04:35,079 --> 00:04:36,279
No one else has touched them.

44
00:04:36,359 --> 00:04:38,359
But I trust Zhao's character.

45
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:39,720
He didn't do it.

46
00:04:41,519 --> 00:04:42,320
Alright.

47
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:44,239
I am aware of this matter now.

48
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,119
Do not let word of this leak out.

49
00:04:46,519 --> 00:04:47,959
What do you plan to do, sir?

50
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:50,079
Xu Linlang

51
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,600
I know you pride yourself on your abilities.

52
00:04:52,799 --> 00:04:55,000
You have always thought I am incompetent.

53
00:04:55,119 --> 00:04:57,040
But I have my own reasons for being in this position today.

54
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:58,640
I have my own way of doing things.

55
00:04:58,880 --> 00:04:59,760
You may go.

56
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:03,440
Then I'll leave it to you, sir.

57
00:05:08,359 --> 00:05:09,359
Useless.

58
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:12,720
You were supposed to poison him so the second young master could fake his death and escape.

59
00:05:13,119 --> 00:05:16,040
Yet you let a mere coroner ruin the plan.

60
00:05:16,279 --> 00:05:17,480
That female coroner, Xu Linlang,

61
00:05:17,559 --> 00:05:18,839
is also doing this for the second young master.

62
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,760
I heard

63
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:22,200
she's still trying to overturn the case for the second young master.

64
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,640
Xu Linlang.

65
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:30,480
Now the prison is sealed off.

66
00:05:30,799 --> 00:05:32,720
As for Lu Jiu being poisoned,

67
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,679
where should I even start investigating?

68
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,040
What's troubling you?

69
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,880
Maybe I can help.

70
00:05:40,279 --> 00:05:41,320
Craftsman.

71
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:42,279
Regular customer.

72
00:05:42,399 --> 00:05:43,600
I can give you a discount.

73
00:05:43,799 --> 00:05:44,799
It's just a pity

74
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:45,959
you can't help me.

75
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:48,160
As long as the price is right,

76
00:05:48,399 --> 00:05:49,760
there's nothing that can't be done.

77
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:52,880
Lu Jiu is in prison.

78
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,320
The real culprit is watching closely.

79
00:05:54,559 --> 00:05:55,359
Tell me,

80
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:57,160
how can I protect him?

81
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,320
Who says there's no way?

82
00:05:59,519 --> 00:06:00,559
At the very least, I can get into the prison.

83
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,799
I can pass a message to your friend.

84
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,600
But this seems... Don't worry.

85
00:06:03,679 --> 00:06:05,119
In our line of work, we do things for money,

86
00:06:05,239 --> 00:06:06,119
but never break the law.

87
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,160
Then I'll leave it to you.

88
00:06:09,279 --> 00:06:10,040
No problem.

89
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,559
But everything

90
00:06:11,799 --> 00:06:13,160
comes with a cost.

91
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,279
As long as I can save Lu Jiu,

92
00:06:19,359 --> 00:06:20,799
I'm willing to spend any amount of money.

93
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:25,559
Take it.

94
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:27,760
I'm a businessman.

95
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:28,880
But I'm not a profiteer.

96
00:06:29,079 --> 00:06:30,440
I only make the money I deserve.

97
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:31,440
Besides,

98
00:06:31,559 --> 00:06:32,799
I'm heading that way anyway.

99
00:06:33,679 --> 00:06:34,559
On the way.

100
00:06:35,119 --> 00:06:36,239
According to the master's instructions,

101
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,679
the pharmacy assistant

102
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:39,320
handed the letter to Xu Linlang,

103
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,679
and it's already been taken care of.

104
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:42,839
Alright.

105
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,920
We absolutely can't let Lu Jiu

106
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:48,200
fall into those people's hands.

107
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,720
Hunting live creatures

108
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,959
is far more interesting than shooting arrows at a target range.

109
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,640
Much more fun.

110
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:58,440
Toying with people's lives in your hands—

111
00:06:58,839 --> 00:07:01,399
that's even more thrilling.

112
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,000
There's one more person.

113
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:21,200
Linlang.

114
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:22,279
What are you doing?

115
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,440
This is the men's mortuary.

116
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:24,640
I was being reckless.

117
00:07:24,679 --> 00:07:25,640
I just wanted to learn from you, big brother.

118
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,040
To learn about autopsy techniques.

119
00:07:27,239 --> 00:07:28,000
I heard that

120
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,720
Lu Mingcheng had gallstones.

121
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:30,640
I wanted to see

122
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:31,440
those gallstones

123
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,279
to see if they're like a monk's relics.

124
00:07:33,359 --> 00:07:35,200
As long as we know how he died, that's enough.

125
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:36,279
Why bother checking that?

126
00:07:36,559 --> 00:07:38,160
Didn't you perform the autopsy?

127
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,799
The condition of the body

128
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:42,119
matches what the Lu family's servants described.

129
00:07:42,239 --> 00:07:44,200
Didn't you also examine that female corpse?

130
00:07:44,279 --> 00:07:45,359
That was Wan Lingling.

131
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:46,440
When they carried her in,

132
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,679
she was still wearing her wedding dress.

133
00:07:47,799 --> 00:07:49,679
Who else could it be but Lu Mingcheng?

134
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,239
Who does such a sloppy autopsy like you?

135
00:07:51,279 --> 00:07:53,239
No, I need to re-examine the body.

136
00:07:53,519 --> 00:07:54,239
Xu Linlang.

137
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:56,200
How many years have you even been a coroner?

138
00:07:56,519 --> 00:07:58,440
I've seen more corpses than you've eaten grains of salt.

139
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,279
Go, go, go.

140
00:07:59,359 --> 00:08:00,279
Sorry, big brother.

141
00:08:00,799 --> 00:08:01,359
Xu Linlang.

142
00:08:01,399 --> 00:08:01,839
What are you doing?

143
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:03,079
Put me down! What are you doing?

144
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,279
Xu Linlang, what are you trying to do?

145
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,079
Let go of me!

146
00:08:06,239 --> 00:08:07,079
Xu Linlang!

147
00:08:07,239 --> 00:08:09,200
You're breaking the law, you know that?

148
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,480
Desperate times call for desperate measures.

149
00:08:10,559 --> 00:08:11,679
Please bear with me.

150
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:33,559
The location matches the medical case provided by the pharmacy.

151
00:08:34,719 --> 00:08:36,359
The deceased is indeed not Lu Mingcheng.

152
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:38,760
Sir.

153
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:41,799
Sir.

154
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,239
Xu Linlang, Xu Linlang.

155
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:45,280
Are you addicted to barging into my study?

156
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,719
I examined the body carefully.

157
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:47,640
That male corpse from the Lu family

158
00:08:47,679 --> 00:08:49,000
is not Lu Mingcheng at all.

159
00:08:52,719 --> 00:08:53,400
That deceased person

160
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:54,640
is not Lu Mingcheng at all.

161
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,960
He is actually the missing servant.

162
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:57,799
But the Lu family’s steward

163
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,760
didn’t mention the disappearance at all.

164
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,440
Wait.

165
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:06,200
You, as a young woman,

166
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,679
examined a male corpse.

167
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,320
That’s against the rules.

168
00:09:09,479 --> 00:09:10,719
If the higher-ups find out,

169
00:09:10,799 --> 00:09:12,080
I’ll be held responsible.

170
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,080
Desperate times call for special measures.

171
00:09:13,159 --> 00:09:14,880
Solving the case comes first. Fine, fine.

172
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:16,799
Stop making it sound so righteous.

173
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,320
You know what kind of person you are

174
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,719
better than anyone.

175
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,599
Don’t you?

176
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:22,679
Besides, as a coroner,

177
00:09:22,719 --> 00:09:23,799
you’re investigating beyond your authority.

178
00:09:24,359 --> 00:09:25,479
If no one keeps you in check,

179
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,200
do you want to take my position?

180
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:28,880
If I’ve done something wrong,

181
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,320
I’m willing to accept punishment.

182
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:32,280
But there are indeed suspicious points in the Lu family’s case.

183
00:09:32,359 --> 00:09:34,440
If you can help Lu Jiu prove his innocence,

184
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:36,440
everyone will praise your wisdom.

185
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:38,440
I don’t need you to tell me how wise I am.

186
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:39,640
Go.

187
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,440
I’ll take my leave now.

188
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:53,599
Sir.

189
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:22,799
How many days has it been?

190
00:10:23,119 --> 00:10:24,000
The seventh day after death.

191
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,159
How do you know?

192
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:34,799
It's my older brother's seventh day.

193
00:10:43,880 --> 00:10:44,799
It was you.

194
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:47,159
We met before on the pleasure boat.

195
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,039
That's right.

196
00:10:49,119 --> 00:10:50,119
Why did you come in here?

197
00:10:50,359 --> 00:10:51,320
Just to get away from the world.

198
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,320
Most of the county jail is unused.

199
00:10:53,359 --> 00:10:54,520
There's no profit to be made here.

200
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:56,799
Some people are willing to pay to stay here for a few days.

201
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,000
To hide from their creditors.

202
00:10:58,239 --> 00:10:59,400
Why wouldn't they do it?

203
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,520
If there's another opportunity like this next time,

204
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:10,880
remember your brother here.

205
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:12,799
What are you looking at?

206
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,239
Just behave yourself.

207
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,200
Please enjoy.

208
00:11:24,679 --> 00:11:26,400
Actually, someone asked me to pass a message to you.

209
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:28,359
Beware of villains poisoning you.

210
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:30,799
Who is it?

211
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,440
I can't reveal my employer's name.

212
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,880
It's my professional code.

213
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:37,159
It's her.

214
00:11:38,159 --> 00:11:39,119
It must be her.

215
00:11:39,679 --> 00:11:41,080
Since I can take money to get in,

216
00:11:41,479 --> 00:11:43,440
I can naturally take money to get you out.

217
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,200
This abyssal prison,

218
00:11:48,479 --> 00:11:49,479
how can one get out?

219
00:11:49,719 --> 00:11:50,760
Someone like me

220
00:11:51,359 --> 00:11:52,400
is better off staying in prison

221
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:54,000
and waiting to die.

222
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,000
The time when the jailers serve food and change shifts

223
00:11:58,679 --> 00:11:59,919
is remembered quite accurately.

224
00:12:02,119 --> 00:12:03,640
Are you trying to report this for credit?

225
00:12:03,799 --> 00:12:05,200
There's no reward for reporting.

226
00:12:05,479 --> 00:12:06,359
It's not worth it.

227
00:12:07,039 --> 00:12:08,679
But helping the wealthy Mr. Lu Jiu

228
00:12:09,039 --> 00:12:10,280
is a different story.

229
00:12:11,919 --> 00:12:13,599
The real culprit wants me dead in prison.

230
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,280
Only by staying alive

231
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:17,919
can I uncover the truth.

232
00:12:27,799 --> 00:12:28,599
Sir

233
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:31,599
What's wrong?

234
00:12:31,719 --> 00:12:32,840
The Lu family's murder case

235
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:34,400
When will it be reviewed again?

236
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:36,440
The evidence in this case is conclusive.

237
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:37,840
There's no need for another review.

238
00:12:38,159 --> 00:12:40,000
But I clearly resubmitted

239
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,400
the autopsy file to you yesterday.

240
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,440
A new autopsy file.

241
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,440
Hmm.

242
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:46,719
I didn't receive it.

243
00:12:47,039 --> 00:12:48,320
If you ignore this,

244
00:12:48,479 --> 00:12:50,039
I'll submit it to the Department of Investigation.

245
00:12:53,119 --> 00:12:53,840
Go ahead.

246
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,400
Is the Department of Investigation

247
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:57,479
somewhere a low-ranking coroner like you can report to?

248
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:58,640
Then I'll go to the Court of Justice.

249
00:12:58,679 --> 00:12:59,640
I'll report it all the way to the Golden Throne.

250
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:01,080
Are you trying to rebel?

251
00:13:02,239 --> 00:13:03,039
I hereby declare

252
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:05,000
that Xu Linlang is stripped of her coroner position.

253
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:07,200
You're not an official

254
00:13:07,479 --> 00:13:08,919
and have no right to participate in the investigation.

255
00:13:09,239 --> 00:13:09,960
Guards!

256
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,080
Throw her out!

257
00:13:13,119 --> 00:13:13,760
Hurry!

258
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:14,559
Yes, sir.

259
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:15,159
You...

260
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,280
You corrupt official!

261
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:18,280
One day, I'll make the truth known to the world!

262
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,559
You corrupt official!

263
00:13:20,159 --> 00:13:20,840
Let go!

264
00:13:21,039 --> 00:13:22,039
Corrupt official!

265
00:13:23,119 --> 00:13:24,159
Shift change.

266
00:13:24,799 --> 00:13:26,119
I'm exhausted.

267
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,520
You know, I have to admit,

268
00:13:34,239 --> 00:13:35,400
the steamed buns in this prison

269
00:13:35,479 --> 00:13:36,520
aren't half bad.

270
00:13:38,679 --> 00:13:39,840
That's more like it.

271
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:40,640
Here,

272
00:13:40,679 --> 00:13:42,479
whether you're a commoner

273
00:13:42,520 --> 00:13:43,840
or a wealthy young master,

274
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:45,760
after a few days of prison food,

275
00:13:45,799 --> 00:13:47,599
even a bun dropped on the ground

276
00:13:47,719 --> 00:13:49,400
starts to smell delicious.

277
00:13:51,599 --> 00:13:53,200
I'm leaving, brother.

278
00:13:54,119 --> 00:13:54,840
What is it?

279
00:13:55,119 --> 00:13:55,919
Changed your mind?

280
00:13:56,159 --> 00:13:57,440
Seizing a jailer

281
