Don't worry about me.

567
00:28:57,719 --> 00:28:58,560
Rest assured.

568
00:28:59,520 --> 00:29:01,000
I will take good care of Linlang.

569
00:29:04,719 --> 00:29:06,079
Shedding one's shell to escape, right.

570
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:07,680
The corpse at the Lu residence

571
00:29:07,800 --> 00:29:08,959
is not Lumingcheng.

572
00:29:09,280 --> 00:29:10,359
The Beggar Sect sent word

573
00:29:10,479 --> 00:29:11,520
that someone paid a large sum

574
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:12,800
to have them deal with the corpse.

575
00:29:12,959 --> 00:29:14,400
Even if Lumingcheng isn't dead,

576
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:15,959
his whereabouts are still unknown.

577
00:29:16,359 --> 00:29:18,079
And the clues point directly to Mist Town.

578
00:29:18,560 --> 00:29:19,319
So Lu Jiu

579
00:29:19,599 --> 00:29:21,359
is our last card.

580
00:29:21,599 --> 00:29:23,439
So as long as we have this card,

581
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:24,640
we still have hope

582
00:29:24,680 --> 00:29:26,599
of finding clues to the Lu family treasure.

583
00:29:27,680 --> 00:29:28,719
However,

584
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:33,160
the authorities already have leads on Lu Jiu.

585
00:29:33,839 --> 00:29:35,920
There must be a spy close to him.

586
00:29:37,520 --> 00:29:38,479
Xu Linlang.

587
00:29:39,079 --> 00:29:39,839
Hmm.

588
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:46,839
Why is he taking so long just to wash his hands?

589
00:29:47,520 --> 00:29:49,599
There were informants even inside the prison.

590
00:29:49,839 --> 00:29:50,599
It's possible

591
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:52,479
he went to meet with that person.

592
00:29:52,800 --> 00:29:55,040
That Sima Kong may have taken my money

593
00:29:55,119 --> 00:29:56,880
to get into the prison and deliver your message,

594
00:29:57,839 --> 00:29:59,400
but since he took such a big risk

595
00:29:59,439 --> 00:30:00,400
to help you escape,

596
00:30:00,520 --> 00:30:01,800
he probably has other motives.

597
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:06,920
Why are you looking at me?

598
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:08,800
So it was you after all.

599
00:30:09,199 --> 00:30:10,520
You warned me someone might use poison.

600
00:30:10,719 --> 00:30:11,520
Yes.

601
00:30:11,839 --> 00:30:13,000
That day in the prison,

602
00:30:13,079 --> 00:30:14,520
you drove me away without listening to a word I said.

603
00:30:14,560 --> 00:30:16,319
How could I dare to warn you after that?

604
00:30:17,520 --> 00:30:18,479
It was all my fault.

605
00:30:18,839 --> 00:30:20,439
I shouldn't have... All right, all right.

606
00:30:20,719 --> 00:30:22,479
If all the evidence pointed to you,

607
00:30:22,560 --> 00:30:24,239
I wouldn't be so sure about you either.

608
00:30:24,359 --> 00:30:25,920
Now we're even.

609
00:30:26,479 --> 00:30:27,160
But...

610
00:30:27,199 --> 00:30:28,760
We still have to watch out for Sima Kong.

611
00:30:28,839 --> 00:30:29,520
Don't worry.

612
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:30,560
I know what I'm doing.

613
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:32,040
I don't know martial arts.

614
00:30:32,359 --> 00:30:33,079
But he

615
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:34,800
has the skills to escape.

616
00:30:35,079 --> 00:30:36,239
If we want to find out the truth,

617
00:30:36,520 --> 00:30:37,400
we need him.

618
00:30:39,839 --> 00:30:40,599
Lu Jiu,

619
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:43,040
I've noticed you're different from before.

620
00:30:44,280 --> 00:30:45,079
Now,

621
00:30:45,479 --> 00:30:46,599
my family is missing,

622
00:30:46,800 --> 00:30:48,239
and I'm accused of murder.

623
00:30:49,520 --> 00:30:50,319
I have already

624
00:30:50,520 --> 00:30:51,959
ceased to be the person I once was.

625
00:30:55,359 --> 00:30:57,199
We only discussed the price for escorting you before.

626
00:30:57,359 --> 00:30:58,239
Investigation and tracking

627
00:30:58,319 --> 00:30:59,439
will cost extra.

628
00:30:59,520 --> 00:31:00,599
Why did you take so long?

629
00:31:01,079 --> 00:31:02,280
I was just going to wash my hands,

630
00:31:02,479 --> 00:31:03,959
but I thought I should get rid of bad luck.

631
00:31:04,040 --> 00:31:05,079
So I changed my clothes.

632
00:31:06,839 --> 00:31:08,599
Young Master Sima really lives up to his name.

633
00:31:08,839 --> 00:31:09,959
Someone even brought you clothes.

634
00:31:10,280 --> 00:31:11,280
You truly are extraordinary.

635
00:31:11,520 --> 00:31:12,680
Same to you.

636
00:31:17,199 --> 00:31:18,000
This way.

637
00:31:19,239 --> 00:31:19,959
Wait.

638
00:31:22,520 --> 00:31:23,119
This way.

639
00:31:24,520 --> 00:31:25,920
Mist Town is in the southeast.

640
00:31:26,439 --> 00:31:27,239
If we take the main road,

641
00:31:27,359 --> 00:31:28,839
it’s not only a detour, but also dangerous.

642
00:31:28,959 --> 00:31:30,199
The authorities probably think the same.

643
00:31:30,560 --> 00:31:32,400
So we’ll do the opposite.

644
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:34,359
Even though it’s a bit of a detour,

645
00:31:34,640 --> 00:31:35,640
we can avoid being pursued.

646
00:31:36,719 --> 00:31:37,560
Just as I said.

647
00:31:37,839 --> 00:31:39,199
You really aren’t an ordinary person.

648
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:43,520
I feel like

649
00:31:43,839 --> 00:31:45,239
he’s hiding a lot from us.

650
00:31:45,959 --> 00:31:47,640
Don’t worry, I’ll protect you.
